    <h3 class="post-title">
	 Christmas Carols
    </h3>
	 
    

         <div class="post-body">

          <p>
      <div style="clear:both;"></div>All four of us participated in our church's Christmas program.  William and Beth learned to play hand bells for a piece that our church choir was singing.  They also played violin, as part of a small string ensemble, with the Christmas carols that were part of the service.<div style="clear:both; padding-bottom:0.25em"></div>
    </p>

        </div>

