  <div class="post"><a name="109041143407798314"></a>

     
	 
    <h3 class="post-title">
	 Baltimore Aquarium
    </h3>
	 
    

         <div class="post-body">

          <p>
      <div style="clear:both;"></div>Over Christmas vacation we went to the Baltimore Aquarium.  The sting ray exhibit was wonderful!  We were able to see their feeding time.  It was great fun to watch the divers swimming with the rays.  We were also able see a diver hand feeding, and petting a small shark.  Very cool stuff.<div style="clear:both; padding-bottom:0.25em"></div>
    </p>

        </div>

        <p class="post-footer">

      <em>posted by Vics @ <a href="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/homeschool-weblog/2004/07/baltimore-aquarium.html" title="permanent link">8:02 AM</a></em> &nbsp;
      
