  <div class="post"><a name="109035151874599532"></a>

     
	 
    <h3 class="post-title">
	 Visiting The Mall
    </h3>
	 
    

         <div class="post-body">

          <p>
      <div style="clear:both;"></div>We had a fun day at the National Mall visiting specific exhibits in the National Gallery, Natural History Museum, and American History Museum.<br /><br /><a href="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/elephant.jpg"><img src="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/elephant.jpg" width="395"></a><br /><br />Fireside Chats<br /><a href="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/firesidechats.JPG"><img src="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/firesidechats.JPG" width="395"></a><div style="clear:both; padding-bottom:0.25em"></div>
    </p>

        </div>

