    <h3 class="post-title">
	 California Trip
    </h3>
	 
    

         <div class="post-body">

          <p>
      <div style="clear:both;"></div>We traveled to California by train in November.  Riding <a href="http://amtrak.com/">Amtrak</a> was an incredible experience.  I think that all four of us are strong believers in traveling by rail now.<br /><a href="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/outsidetrain.jpg"><img src="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/outsidetrain.jpg" width="395"></a><br /><br />Beth made a newt out of some <a href="http://www.thinkgeek.com/cubegoodies/toys/5ac8/">Thinking Putty</a>.<br /><a href="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/bethontrain.jpg"><img src="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/bethontrain.jpg" width="395"></a><br /><br />We visited the Pacific Ocean and the <a href="http://www.usc.edu/isd/archives/la/historic/san_fernando_mission.html"><em>San Fernando Mission</em></a> while we were there.<br /><a href="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/atbeach.jpg"><img src="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/atbeach.jpg" width="395"></a><div style="clear:both; padding-bottom:0.25em"></div>
    </p>

        </div>

        <p class="post-footer">

      <em>posted by Vics @ <a href="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/homeschool-weblog/2004/07/california-trip.html" title="permanent link">2:44 PM</a></em> &nbsp;
      
