  <div class="post"><a name="109033889033699712"></a>

     
	 
    <h3 class="post-title">
	 Weed Force - Germantown Station
    </h3>
	 
    

         <div class="post-body">

          <p>
      <div style="clear:both;"></div>In September we were studying about roots in science class.  After pulling a few weeds at home  and sorting them by fibrous and tuberous types, we decided to take our investigations on the road.  We had noticed earlier that the train station near us was badly in need of some weeding help.  Calling ourselves <em>Weed Force</em>, after the BBC America TV show <a href="http://www.bbcamerica.com/genre/home_living/ground_force/ground_force_about_the_show.jsp"><em>Ground Force</em></a>, we decended on the quiet unsuspecting station and performed a bit of a makeover.<br /><br />This is how it looked when we arrived.<br /><a href="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/1station2003.jpg"><img src="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/1station2003.jpg" width="395"></a><br /><br />One large weed required the effort of both William and Beth.<br /><a href="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/2station2003.jpg"><img src="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/2station2003.jpg" width="395"></a><br /><br />They were finally victorious!<br /><a href="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/3station2003.jpg"><img src="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/3station2003.jpg" width="395"></a><br /><br />This is how it looked when were finished.  We filled three, large, yard waste bags full to the brim with weeds that morning.<br /><a href="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/4station2003.jpg"><img src="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/pix/schoolblogpics/4station2003.jpg" width="395"></a><br /><div style="clear:both; padding-bottom:0.25em"></div>
    </p>

        </div>

        <p class="post-footer">

      <em>posted by Vics @ <a href="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/homeschool-weblog/2004/07/weed-force-germantown-station.html" title="permanent link">11:49 AM</a></em> &nbsp;
      
         <a class="comment-link" href="http://vicki.ashtonfam.org/homeschool-weblog/2004/07/weed-force-germantown-station.html#comments">0 comments</a>
